WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.803
Setting up Mom's phone usually takes an hour. ScamRadar does it in one tap.

00:00:06.943 --> 00:00:15.511
On your phone, generate a QR code. Name them. Add your number. Done.

00:00:15.651 --> 00:00:20.835
Hand them the screen. They open ScamRadar and scan.

00:00:20.975 --> 00:00:33.733
Care Mode turns on. The pod joins. Your number becomes their emergency contact. One tap. Confirm. Done.

00:00:33.873 --> 00:00:41.961
Every scam she runs into shows up in your weekly digest. Every scam she catches helps the whole pod.

00:00:42.101 --> 00:00:46.935
Help a relative in 30 seconds. Not an hour.
